com.cyc.kb.client

Class SymbolImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.kb.client.KBObjectImpl
      • com.cyc.kb.client.SymbolImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KBObject, Symbol

    public class SymbolImpl
extends KBObjectImpl
implements Symbol
    A Symbol object is a facade for a quoted instance of #$CycLSubLSymbol in Cyc KB. This class of objects are used in construction of sentences with replacement arguments, for example in stored queries for testing. The usage of this is rare, but the API supports it for completeness.
